Date: Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:30:39 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 91/95] backend-drm: Skip gamma reset by default

Set env "WESTON_DRM_RESET_GAMMA" to enable it.

Signed-off-by: Jeffy Chen <jeffy.chen@rock-chips.com>
---
 libweston/backend-drm/kms.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/libweston/backend-drm/kms.c b/libweston/backend-drm/kms.c
index 16c07b0..f84ac84 100644
--- a/libweston/backend-drm/kms.c
+++ b/libweston/backend-drm/kms.c
@@ -817,6 +817,9 @@ drm_output_reset_legacy_gamma(struct drm_output *output)
 	uint32_t i;
 	int ret;
 
+	if (!getenv("WESTON_DRM_RESET_GAMMA"))
+		return;
+
 	if (len == 0)
 		return;
 
